io.github.yappy.lua.lib

Annotation Type LuaLibraryFunction


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface LuaLibraryFunction
    Annotated field is library function. name() is function name. args() declares arguments specification. Arguments will be automatically checked and converted following it.
    Author:
    yappy
    See Also:
    LuaEngine.openLibrary(LuaLibrary), LuaLibraryTable, LuaArg
